  why "검증코드 없는 논문 = 미완성" (n6shared absolute_rules N62 / PP2) AND "3-pack 누락 = 미완성" (SSCB mk1 reference: brief PDF §1-§7 + engineering PDF §8-§20 + impact PDF §21 = single .md source). mk1 .own had own#6 (verify-embed) + own#15 (21-section) as separate rules; mk2 collapses them into one unified rule mirroring hive raw.mk2 arch.001 pattern (4-rule cluster -> 1 canonical pattern). Mathematical OR physical classification gate added per 2026-05-03 user directive ("수학적, 물리적 검증코드여야한다") — auto-detect required (Tier-1 substring + Tier-2 AST fallback). Deep research (2026-05-03) confirmed: 158/164 papers (96.3%) already scaffold §1-§21 + mk_history; 148/164 (90.2%) already have ```python block; 135/148 (91.2%) match math template signature. Reconstruction is declarative SSOT recovery; enforcement layer (own#15 lint + classifier) deferred to follow-up cycle.
  invariant brief-§1-§7 — ## §1 WHY / ## §2 COMPARE / ## §3 REQUIRES / ## §4 STRUCT / ## §5 FLOW / ## §6 EVOLVE / ## §7 VERIFY headers all present
  invariant engineering-§8-§20 — ## §8 EXEC SUMMARY / ## §9 SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS / ## §10 ARCHITECTURE / ## §11 CIRCUIT DESIGN / ## §12 PCB DESIGN / ## §13 FIRMWARE / ## §14 MECHANICAL / ## §15 MANUFACTURING / ## §16 TEST / ## §17 BOM / ## §18 VENDOR / ## §19 ACCEPTANCE / ## §20 APPENDIX headers all present
  invariant impact-§21 — ## §21 IMPACT header present
  invariant python-block-embedded — ```python ... ``` fenced block >=1 inside §7 VERIFY (substring check; sibling .py/.hexa verify file FORBIDDEN per mk1 own#6)
  invariant math-or-physics-classified — python block content classifies as math OR physics OR both:
    math signatures: def sigma\b | def divisors\b | def sopfr\b | def phi_min_prime | def totient\b | from math import gcd | divisor_sigma | _totient | is_squarefree | Fraction | n6_master | divisor_count | sympy
    physics signatures: NIST | CODATA | Carnot | Shockley | Queisser | Bernoulli | Weibull | Darcy | Kozeny | Helmholtz | Eigen-Hammes | scientific notation [0-9]+\.[0-9]+e-?[0-9]+ | SI units (mΩ|kHz|MHz|GHz|nm|μm|μs|ns|ms|eV|J/K|kg/m³|Wh/kg)
    classify=neither -> FAIL (decorative / tautology block forbidden; cross-fire with own#31 v3.19)
  invariant mk_history-footer — ## mk_history (underscore form; 158/164 papers use this) header + >=3 lines (Mk.I / Mk.II / Mk.III ...) at footer
